title: Dylan's 60's Albums
description:
This includes Dylan's first nine studio albums: Bob Dylan, (1962), The Freewheelin' Bob Dylan, (1963), The Times They Are a-Changing, Another Side of Bob Dylan, (1964), Bringing It All Back Home, Highway 61 Revisited, (1965), Blonde On Blonde, (1966), John Wesley Harding, (1967), and Nashville Skyline, (1969.) Thus, it covers his career from his arrival in New York as a disciple of Woodie Guthrie, his ascension to being 'the voice of his generation,' (a title he despised), through his motorcycle crash and self-imposed exile, culminating with his re-invention of himself as a country music artist.  

Please check out my other torrents, including a Dylan album sampler, which includes songs from all 37 of his studio albums...
